---
const id = "terminal-policy";

const fullCopy = `IMPORTANT. MUST READ. EYES ONLY.

This project accepts voluntary donations only.

Donations are used to directly support:
• ongoing development
• infrastructure and hosting
• documentation and research
• the developers themselves

No corporate quid-pro-quo.
No government funding.
No influence payments.

No ROI. No equity. No control.

This is not an investment vehicle.
This is independent development.

The system is designed for people.
Transparency is intentional.

End of policy transmission.`;
---

<section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5 shadow-[0_0_0_1px_rgba(255,255,255,0.04)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
  <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60">
    Donation Policy
  </div>

  <div class="mt-3 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-black/30 p-4 md:p-5">
    <pre class="m-0 overflow-x-auto text-sm leading-6 text-white/90 md:text-[15px]">
<code
  id={id}
  class="block min-h-[12rem] whitespace-pre-wrap"
  aria-live="polite"
  aria-label="Donation policy terminal"
></code><span class="terminal-cursor align-baseline">█</span>
    </pre>

    <div class="sr-only">
      <h2>Donation Policy</h2>
      <pre>{fullCopy}</pre>
    </div>

    <noscript>
      <pre class="mt-4 whitespace-pre-wrap text-white/90">{fullCopy}</pre>
    </noscript>
  </div>

  <style>
    .terminal-cursor {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-left: 2px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      animation: blink 1.1s steps(1, end) infinite;
    }
    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 49% { opacity: 0.9; }
      50%, 100% { opacity: 0.0; }
    }
  </style>

  <script defer src="/js/terminalPolicyClient.js"></script>
</section>
